<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3365879>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Herrera phyllodes n. sp.: A, holotype male and paratype female habitus; B, holotype male dorsum; C, paratype male timbal; D, paratype male operculum; E, paratype female operculum; F, holotype male lateral view of genitalia; G, holotype male posterior view of genitalia; H, paratype female lateral view of genitalia; I, paratype female ventral view of genitalia. Scale bar: A, 2 cm; B, 2 mm; C–I, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3365879/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

